# Verification Checklist - Firebase Hosting Sandbox

## Quick Start

### 1. Start Firebase Emulator
```bash
firebase emulators:start --only hosting
```

### 2. Open URLs in Browser

Test these URLs (replace port if different):
- `http://127.0.0.1:5000/` (or port shown in terminal)
- `http://127.0.0.1:5000/tools`
- `http://127.0.0.1:5000/tools.html`
- `http://127.0.0.1:5000/insights`
- `http://127.0.0.1:5000/insights.html`
- `http://127.0.0.1:5000/about/`
- `http://127.0.0.1:5000/store/`
- `http://127.0.0.1:5000/disclosures/`
- `http://127.0.0.1:5000/ethics/`
- `http://127.0.0.1:5000/analytics/`
- `http://127.0.0.1:5000/terms/`

## Chrome DevTools Verification

### Network Tab → Filter by "CSS"

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ `main.css` → Status 200
- ✅ `integrated.css` → Status 200
- ❌ No 404 errors for CSS files

### Console Tab

**Expected Output (localhost only):**
```
=== CSS Loading Debug (Localhost) ===
Stylesheet links found: 2
Stylesheet link 1: http://127.0.0.1:5000/css/main.css
Stylesheet link 2: http://127.0.0.1:5000/css/integrated.css
====================================
```

## Visual Verification

### Desktop
- ✅ Header navigation visible and styled
- ✅ Footer visible and styled
- ✅ Content properly formatted
- ✅ Colors match live site
- ✅ Typography matches live site
- ✅ Spacing and layout correct

### Mobile (DevTools → Toggle Device Toolbar)
- ✅ Responsive layout works
- ✅ Navigation accessible
- ✅ Text readable
- ✅ No horizontal scrolling

## Route Verification

### Clean URLs (without .html)
- ✅ `/tools` loads `tools.html`
- ✅ `/insights` loads `insights.html`
- ✅ `/about/` loads `about/index.html`
- ✅ `/store/` loads `store/index.html`

### Direct URLs (with .html)
- ✅ `/tools.html` loads correctly
- ✅ `/insights.html` loads correctly

