## Success Criteria

✅ **PASS** if:
- All CSS files load with 200 status
- Page styling matches live site
- All routes work (with and without .html)
- Console shows debug output on localhost only
- No 404 errors in Network tab

❌ **FAIL** if:
- Any CSS file returns 404
- Page appears unstyled
- Routes don't work
- Console errors appear

